x4freetext: PR,B133,323,1964 to PR,133,B323,1964 as it coded in
.A Counter telescope consisting of a silicon
p-n function diode preceded by a gas proportional
counter with offset center wire. Pulses from the Gas
Proportional Counter -dE/dx pulses- and from the
Sillicon counter -E pulses- are fed into a multiplier
network, output pulses of the latter identify detected
particles as protons, deuterons or alpha particles.
